t; `i` is used. We can guess, but I prefer more explicit over guessing.<br></p><p>? it&#39;s in the base name and argument labels, not to mention the types.<br>All the information available at the use-site, and more, is there in the<br>declaration.<br></p><p><br>-- <br>-Dave<br></p></div></li></ul></div>    </main>
